name: Nami (ナミ) One Piece Character LoRA (Post-timeskip)
description:
V3 update note: This is the Final version. From the time i posted the previous version of this LoRA i have gained experience on how to make my LoRA's better, so this is me fixing my previous mistakes. All models of main/side-main characters of One Piece will receive a similar amount of attention from me :)

Trained on AnyLora

To get the best results, please read the description below:

  • For V3.0:

    • Recommended weight: 0.6-0.8

    • Activation word: NamiV3

  • For V2.0:

    • Recommended weight: 0.7-0.85

    • Activation word: NamiV2

  • For V1.0:

    • Recommended weight: 0.7-0.9

    • Activation word: NamiChan

  • Upscale to 1.5

  • To avoid her tattoo appearing on the right shoulder or on both, use such negative prompts as: (right shoulder tattoo, multiple tattoos)

I would appreciate any reviews, positive or negative!

If you have any suggestions on what LoRA i should do next, please share them in the comments

Enjoy :)
